snippet.title: Night Outside The Bank, Inconvenience Only For Short Time, Many Hope

localized.description:
The desperate rush for cash continued a week after the government in a surprise announcement scrapped Rs. 500 and 1,000 notes in a bid to crack down on corruption. People scrambling for cash were seen queuing outside banks and ATMs since late last night.
